snippet.title: Spud Customs - Official Narrative Trailer | Underground Potato Document Thriller Game
snippet.description:
Unearth dark secrets in the tuber underworld...

Something's rotten in the Root Reserve. As quotas rise and suspicions grow, navigate a society of potato people caught in a web of corruption and conspiracy.

Wishlist Spud Customs on Steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3291880/Spud_Customs/

A narrative thriller where every spud has something to hide.

#SpudCustoms #IndieGames #NarrativeThriller #IndieGameDev #Gaming
